list.name: Default
list.comment:
Added banks and models for category, routine, routine category, exercise
Changed structure of activities to nest beneath exercise category, need to test how we can add an exercise of the same category lower in the training, maybe we don't nest it this way.
Also cleaned up all html in pre main and post, and dismissed on save when saving training

task.summary:
Created exercise table model
Current model structure: Training > mainTraining > Activities > Exercises > ExerciseTable > Labels, ExerciseName, Sets, etc.
Currently can add exercise table as hard code with flexibility of adding different labels
Added connection and binding the set of exercise table, still need to fix styling on table
Short term commit before overhaul and push, now working on exercise categories

Added banks and models for category, routine, routine category, exercise

Also cleaned up all html in pre main and post, and dismissed on save when saving training
added bank provider ExerciseProvider to retrieve banks and update them two new pages for create and add exercise, and two more for selecting category and table type
Can now add new exercises to exercisebank in ExerciseProvider, seachQuery on add exercise page also updates, need to autoselect and clear searchBar on creation of new exercise still
Added create new exercise flow with modals and banks of exercises and categories, need to update table types still to be more descriptive of what they contain
Before making a million changes because exercises will be ExerciseTable[] beneath mainCalEvent
all exercise tables listed beneath categories, provider updated to push only the information we need in the database
